hh3cDvpn.name: hh3cDvpn
hh3cDvpn.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
hh3cDvpn.description: This MIB is Dynamic Virtual Private Network(Dvpn) mib. This MIB is applicable to router. Some objects in this may be used only for some specific products, so users should refer to the related documents to acquire more detail information.

DvpnAlgorithmSuite.name: DvpnAlgorithmSuite
DvpnAlgorithmSuite.description: 13 kinds of dvpn algorithms. encryption method | hash method | key width. dvpnDesCbcMd5PreShaModp768: des | md5 | 768 dvpnDesCbcMd5PreShaModp1024: des | md5 | 1024 dvpnDesCbcSha1PreShaModp768: des | sha1 | 768 dvpnDesCbcSha1PreShaModp1024: des | sha1 | 1024 dvpn3DesCbcMd5PreShaModp768: 3des | md5 | 768 dvpn3DesCbcMd5PreShaModp1024: 3des | md5 | 1024 dvpn3DesCbcSha1PreShaModp768: 3des | sha1 | 768 dvpn3DesCbcSha1PreShaModp1024: 3des | sha1 | 1024 dvpnAesCbcMd5PreShaModp768: Aes | md5 | 768 dvpnAesCbcMd5PreShaModp1024: Aes | md5 | 1024 dvpnAesCbcSHA1Sha1PreShaModp768: Aes | sha1 | 768 dvpnAesCbcSHA1Sha1PreShaModp1024: Aes | sha1 | 1024 dvpnAlgorithmNone: none | none | no key

DvpnCommunicateType.name: DvpnCommunicateType
DvpnCommunicateType.description: The type of the communication between client and server. It indicates the direction of the communication.

hh3cDvpnServiceEnable.name: hh3cDvpnServiceEnable
hh3cDvpnServiceEnable.description: Dvpn service enable or disable. If dvpn service is 'disable', dvpn service can not be used.

hh3cDvpnClassNumber.name: hh3cDvpnClassNumber
hh3cDvpnClassNumber.description: The number of dvpn classes. It is only used on client.

hh3cDvpnClientNumber.name: hh3cDvpnClientNumber
hh3cDvpnClientNumber.description: The number of clients which register on the server. When a session of server to client type is built, add 1 to the value of this node. It is only used on server.

hh3cDvpnMapAgeTime.name: hh3cDvpnMapAgeTime
hh3cDvpnMapAgeTime.description: Dvpn map age time, the unit is second. It is only used on server.

hh3cDvpnClientRegisterInterval.name: hh3cDvpnClientRegisterInterval
hh3cDvpnClientRegisterInterval.description: The length of time between the registering of client, the unit is second. It is only used on client.

hh3cDvpnClientRegisterDumb.name: hh3cDvpnClientRegisterDumb
hh3cDvpnClientRegisterDumb.description: The length of time when client dumbs, the unit is second. It is only used on client.

hh3cDvpnClientRegisterRetry.name: hh3cDvpnClientRegisterRetry
hh3cDvpnClientRegisterRetry.description: Regist retry times of client after register fail. It is only used on client.

hh3cDvpnDropPkt.name: hh3cDvpnDropPkt
hh3cDvpnDropPkt.description: The number of packets have been droped.

hh3cDvpnOutputPkt.name: hh3cDvpnOutputPkt
hh3cDvpnOutputPkt.description: The number of packets have been sent.

hh3cDvpnOutputErrorPkt.name: hh3cDvpnOutputErrorPkt
hh3cDvpnOutputErrorPkt.description: The number of output error packets.

hh3cDvpnEncryptErrorPkt.name: hh3cDvpnEncryptErrorPkt
hh3cDvpnEncryptErrorPkt.description: The number of packets have been encrypted wrongly.

hh3cDvpnCurrentDeviceRole.name: hh3cDvpnCurrentDeviceRole
hh3cDvpnCurrentDeviceRole.description: The current role of the device. The value is decided by the configuration of the tunnel-interface.

hh3cDvpnSessionNumber.name: hh3cDvpnSessionNumber
hh3cDvpnSessionNumber.description: The number of dvpn sessiones including the session of all states.

hh3cDvpnServerPreSharedKey.name: hh3cDvpnServerPreSharedKey
hh3cDvpnServerPreSharedKey.description: The pre-shared-key of server. It is only used on server.

hh3cDvpnMapTrapEnable.name: hh3cDvpnMapTrapEnable
hh3cDvpnMapTrapEnable.description: Dvpn map trap enable or disable.

hh3cDvpnSessionTrapEnable.name: hh3cDvpnSessionTrapEnable
hh3cDvpnSessionTrapEnable.description: Dvpn session trap enable or disable.

hh3cDvpnClearDomainAllConection.name: hh3cDvpnClearDomainAllConection
hh3cDvpnClearDomainAllConection.description: Clear all dvpn conects in the domain, the parameter is the id of the domain.

hh3cDvpnClearDvpnStaInfo.name: hh3cDvpnClearDvpnStaInfo
hh3cDvpnClearDvpnStaInfo.description: Clear the statistic information of dvpn.

hh3cDvpnTotalRedirectNumber.name: hh3cDvpnTotalRedirectNumber
hh3cDvpnTotalRedirectNumber.description: The number of redirect packets. It is only used on server.

hh3cDvpnGlobalAuthenClientType.name: hh3cDvpnGlobalAuthenClientType
hh3cDvpnGlobalAuthenClientType.description: Dvpn global authentication type being used by server to client. The value is decided by the configuration by the user.

hh3cDvpnGlobalUserDefAAADomain.name: hh3cDvpnGlobalUserDefAAADomain
hh3cDvpnGlobalUserDefAAADomain.description: Dvpn global AAA domain of the user. The domain will decide the authentication server which is used by the dvpn server to authenticate dvpn client.

hh3cDvpnLocalDeviceId.name: hh3cDvpnLocalDeviceId
hh3cDvpnLocalDeviceId.description: The device ID, it is a string.

hh3cDvpnSessionHisAgeTime.name: hh3cDvpnSessionHisAgeTime
hh3cDvpnSessionHisAgeTime.description: The age-time of the hh3cDvpnSessionHisTable table. The unit is hour.

hh3cDvpnSessionHisReset.name: hh3cDvpnSessionHisReset
hh3cDvpnSessionHisReset.description: The reset flag of dvpn hh3cDvpnSessionHisTable table.

hh3cDvpnPolicyTable.name: hh3cDvpnPolicyTable
hh3cDvpnPolicyTable.description: The dvpn policy table. It is used on dvpn server.

hh3cDvpnPoAuthenClientType.name: hh3cDvpnPoAuthenClientType
hh3cDvpnPoAuthenClientType.description: The authentication type used by server to client. The value is decided by the policy configuration of the user. The default value is none.

hh3cDvpnPoSessionAlgorithmSuite.name: hh3cDvpnPoSessionAlgorithmSuite
hh3cDvpnPoSessionAlgorithmSuite.description: The algorithm suite used when session is created.

hh3cDvpnPoSessionIdleTime.name: hh3cDvpnPoSessionIdleTime
hh3cDvpnPoSessionIdleTime.description: The session idle time, the unit is second.

hh3cDvpnPoSessionKeepTime.name: hh3cDvpnPoSessionKeepTime
hh3cDvpnPoSessionKeepTime.description: The session keepalive time, the unit is second.

hh3cDvpnPoSessionSetupInterval.name: hh3cDvpnPoSessionSetupInterval
hh3cDvpnPoSessionSetupInterval.description: The session setup interval time, the unit is second.

hh3cDvpnPoDataAlgorithmSuite.name: hh3cDvpnPoDataAlgorithmSuite
hh3cDvpnPoDataAlgorithmSuite.description: The algorithm suite used by the session for createing ipsec sa.

hh3cDvpnPoSaSeconds.name: hh3cDvpnPoSaSeconds
hh3cDvpnPoSaSeconds.description: The duration of DVPN IPSec security association. The unit is second.

hh3cDvpnPoUserDefAAADomain.name: hh3cDvpnPoUserDefAAADomain
hh3cDvpnPoUserDefAAADomain.description: Dvpn policy AAA domain of the user. The domain will decide the authentication server which used by the dvpn server to authenticate dvpn client.

hh3cDvpnPoRefTimes.name: hh3cDvpnPoRefTimes
hh3cDvpnPoRefTimes.description: The total times of the policy being used by dvpn.

hh3cDvpnPoRowStatus.name: hh3cDvpnPoRowStatus
hh3cDvpnPoRowStatus.description: The status of this conceptual row. We support the characteristic of active(1),createAndGo(4),destroy(6).

hh3cDvpnDomainSessionNum.name: hh3cDvpnDomainSessionNum
hh3cDvpnDomainSessionNum.description: The number of session in this dvpn domain.

hh3cDvpnDomainRedirectNum.name: hh3cDvpnDomainRedirectNum
hh3cDvpnDomainRedirectNum.description: The number of redirect packets in this dvpn domain.

hh3cDvpnDomainInputPkt.name: hh3cDvpnDomainInputPkt
hh3cDvpnDomainInputPkt.description: The number of input packets in this dvpn domain.

hh3cDvpnDomainDropPkt.name: hh3cDvpnDomainDropPkt
hh3cDvpnDomainDropPkt.description: The number of drop packets in this dvpn domain.

hh3cDvpnDomainOutputPkt.name: hh3cDvpnDomainOutputPkt
hh3cDvpnDomainOutputPkt.description: The number of output packets in this dvpn domain.

hh3cDvpnDomainOutputErrorPkt.name: hh3cDvpnDomainOutputErrorPkt
hh3cDvpnDomainOutputErrorPkt.description: The number of output error packets in this dvpn domain.

hh3cDvpnDomainEncryptErrorPkt.name: hh3cDvpnDomainEncryptErrorPkt
hh3cDvpnDomainEncryptErrorPkt.description: The number of encrypt error packets in this dvpn domain.

hh3cDvpnClassTable.name: hh3cDvpnClassTable
hh3cDvpnClassTable.description: The Dvpn class table. It is only used on dvpn client.

hh3cDvpnClassName.name: hh3cDvpnClassName
hh3cDvpnClassName.description: The dvpn class name. It is the index of hh3cDvpnClassTable.

hh3cDvpnClServerPublicIpType.name: hh3cDvpnClServerPublicIpType
hh3cDvpnClServerPublicIpType.description: Dvpn server public ip type (ipv4, ipv6).

hh3cDvpnClServerPriIpType.name: hh3cDvpnClServerPriIpType
hh3cDvpnClServerPriIpType.description: Dvpn server private ip type (ipv4, ipv6).

hh3cDvpnClAlgorithmSuite.name: hh3cDvpnClAlgorithmSuite
hh3cDvpnClAlgorithmSuite.description: The algorithm suite used by the client when sending registry packets to the server. 'dvpnAlgorithmNone' is not supported here.

hh3cDvpnClAuthenServerType.name: hh3cDvpnClAuthenServerType
hh3cDvpnClAuthenServerType.description: The authentication type being used by client to server. The value is decided by the class configuration of the user. The default value is none.

hh3cDvpnClPreShareKey.name: hh3cDvpnClPreShareKey
hh3cDvpnClPreShareKey.description: Dvpn PreShareKey. It is used when the method used by client when authenticating server is pre-share-key, only when the value of the key is the same as that on the server, the client can authenticate server successfully.

hh3cDvpnClUserName.name: hh3cDvpnClUserName
hh3cDvpnClUserName.description: Dvpn UserName. It is configured by the user.

hh3cDvpnClPasswd.name: hh3cDvpnClPasswd
hh3cDvpnClPasswd.description: Dvpn password. It is configured by the user.

hh3cDvpnClassRowStatus.name: hh3cDvpnClassRowStatus
hh3cDvpnClassRowStatus.description: The status of this conceptual row. Only 'active', 'createAndGo' and 'destroy' are supported.

hh3cDvpnTunnelInterfaceType.name: hh3cDvpnTunnelInterfaceType
hh3cDvpnTunnelInterfaceType.description: The type of dvpn tunnel (client or server).

hh3cDvpnTunnelAcl.name: hh3cDvpnTunnelAcl
hh3cDvpnTunnelAcl.description: The security acl used by the tunnel. If a packet permits the rules, it will not be encrypted.

hh3cDvpnTunnelClientRegType.name: hh3cDvpnTunnelClientRegType
hh3cDvpnTunnelClientRegType.description: The register type used by the client . Only the interface type is client, it can be used. undistributed: If a client send a packet to the client with this configuration, setver will only forward the packet whitout sending redirect packets. forward: The client with this configuration will only send packets forwarded by server, which means it can not initiate to build a session with other clients. undistributedandforward: The client with this configuration have the characteristics of both 'forward' and 'undistributed'. normal: The client with this configuration can build session with other clients without any restriction.

hh3cDvpnTunnelDvpnId.name: hh3cDvpnTunnelDvpnId
hh3cDvpnTunnelDvpnId.description: The dvpn ID used by the tunnel. The dvpn ID is 0 means that user does not configure dvpn ID. User can not configure a dvpn ID with 0.

hh3cDvpnTunnelPolicy.name: hh3cDvpnTunnelPolicy
hh3cDvpnTunnelPolicy.description: The dvpn policy used by the tunnel. Only the interface type is server, it can be used.

hh3cDvpnTunnelClass.name: hh3cDvpnTunnelClass
hh3cDvpnTunnelClass.description: The dvpn class used by the tunnel. Only the interface type is client, it can be used.

hh3cDvpnMapPeerDeviceId.name: hh3cDvpnMapPeerDeviceId
hh3cDvpnMapPeerDeviceId.description: The identifier of peer device. It is a string.

hh3cDvpnMapDvpnId.name: hh3cDvpnMapDvpnId
hh3cDvpnMapDvpnId.description: The ID of the dvpn domain which the map belongs to. The dvpn ID is 0 means that the map has not been built. It has not gotten the dvpn ID at that time.

hh3cDvpnMapBuildTime.name: hh3cDvpnMapBuildTime
hh3cDvpnMapBuildTime.description: The time of the map created, the unit is second.

hh3cDvpnMapPeerPriIpType.name: hh3cDvpnMapPeerPriIpType
hh3cDvpnMapPeerPriIpType.description: The private ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of map peer device.

hh3cDvpnMapPeerPriIp.name: hh3cDvpnMapPeerPriIp
hh3cDvpnMapPeerPriIp.description: The private ip of map peer device.

hh3cDvpnMapPeerPublicIpType.name: hh3cDvpnMapPeerPublicIpType
hh3cDvpnMapPeerPublicIpType.description: The public ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of map peer device.

hh3cDvpnMapPeerPublicIp.name: hh3cDvpnMapPeerPublicIp
hh3cDvpnMapPeerPublicIp.description: The public ip of map peer device.

hh3cDvpnMapLocalPriIpType.name: hh3cDvpnMapLocalPriIpType
hh3cDvpnMapLocalPriIpType.description: The private ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of map local device.

hh3cDvpnMapLocalPriIp.name: hh3cDvpnMapLocalPriIp
hh3cDvpnMapLocalPriIp.description: The private ip of map local device.

hh3cDvpnMapLocalPublicIpType.name: hh3cDvpnMapLocalPublicIpType
hh3cDvpnMapLocalPublicIpType.description: The public ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of map local device.

hh3cDvpnMapLocalPublicIp.name: hh3cDvpnMapLocalPublicIp
hh3cDvpnMapLocalPublicIp.description: The public ip of map local device.

hh3cDvpnMapUserName.name: hh3cDvpnMapUserName
hh3cDvpnMapUserName.description: The user name used by the client registering to server. If the client is not been authenticated, this is a null string.

hh3cDvpnMapUdpPort.name: hh3cDvpnMapUdpPort
hh3cDvpnMapUdpPort.description: The udp port used by map peer device.

hh3cDvpnMapType.name: hh3cDvpnMapType
hh3cDvpnMapType.description: The type of the map. 'clientToclient' is not supported here.

hh3cDvpnMapState.name: hh3cDvpnMapState
hh3cDvpnMapState.description: mapClientInit: The client initiates the map. mapClientBegin: The client begins the process of registering to the server. mapClientAlgreq: The client requests to negotiate the algorithm. mapClientKexReq: The client requests to negotiate the key. mapClientAuthenReq: The client sends authentication information to the server. mapClientConfigReq: The client requests to get some configuration information from the server. Do not support now. mapClientReq: The client requests to register to the server. mapClientSuccess: The client registers to the server successfully. mapServerBegin: The server begins the process of receive a new register. mapServerAlgorithm:The sever begins to negotiate Algorithm. mapServerKexInit: The server replys to the algorithm negotiation packet from the client successfully and begin to negotiate key. mapServerAuthenInit: The server replys to the key negotiation packet from the client successfully and begin to authenticate client, in the case of the authentication-client method is not none. mapServerConfigInit: The server send some configuration information to client. Do not support now. mapServerInit: The server replys to the authentication packet from the client successfully and begin to receive client information. mapServerFinished: The server receives client information successfully.

hh3cDvpnSessionDvpnId.name: hh3cDvpnSessionDvpnId
hh3cDvpnSessionDvpnId.description: The ID of the dvpn domain which the session belongs to.

hh3cDvpnSessionPeerPriIpType.name: hh3cDvpnSessionPeerPriIpType
hh3cDvpnSessionPeerPriIpType.description: The private ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of session peer device.

hh3cDvpnSessionPeerPriIp.description: The private ip of the session peer device.

hh3cDvpnSessionPeerDeviceId.name: hh3cDvpnSessionPeerDeviceId
hh3cDvpnSessionPeerDeviceId.description: The device ID of session peer device. It is a string.

hh3cDvpnSessionBuildTime.name: hh3cDvpnSessionBuildTime
hh3cDvpnSessionBuildTime.description: The time of the Session being built, the unit is second.

hh3cDvpnSessionPeerPubIpType.name: hh3cDvpnSessionPeerPubIpType
hh3cDvpnSessionPeerPubIpType.description: The public ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of session peer device.

hh3cDvpnSessionPeerPubIp.name: hh3cDvpnSessionPeerPubIp
hh3cDvpnSessionPeerPubIp.description: The public ip of session peer device.

hh3cDvpnSessionLocalPubIpType.name: hh3cDvpnSessionLocalPubIpType
hh3cDvpnSessionLocalPubIpType.description: The public ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of session local device.

hh3cDvpnSessionLocalPubIp.name: hh3cDvpnSessionLocalPubIp
hh3cDvpnSessionLocalPubIp.description: The public ip of session local device.

hh3cDvpnSessionLocalPriIpType.name: hh3cDvpnSessionLocalPriIpType
hh3cDvpnSessionLocalPriIpType.description: The private ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of session local device.

hh3cDvpnSessionLocalPriIp.name: hh3cDvpnSessionLocalPriIp
hh3cDvpnSessionLocalPriIp.description: The private ip of session local device.

hh3cDvpnSessionPeerUdpPort.name: hh3cDvpnSessionPeerUdpPort
hh3cDvpnSessionPeerUdpPort.description: The udp port used by session peer device .

hh3cDvpnSessionUserName.name: hh3cDvpnSessionUserName
hh3cDvpnSessionUserName.description: The user's name. If the session type is client to client, the value of this object is a null string.

hh3cDvpnSessionState.name: hh3cDvpnSessionState
hh3cDvpnSessionState.description: The state of the session. sessionSetupInit: The initiation of the session. sessionSetupReq: The initiator requests to negotiate the SA and so on of the session. sessionSetupSuccess: The session has been built successfully. sessionRekeyReq: The initiator requests to renegotiate the SA. sessionRekeyRep: The passive side replies with a SA renegotiation response packet successfully.

hh3cDvpnSessionPeerType.name: hh3cDvpnSessionPeerType
hh3cDvpnSessionPeerType.description: The type of the session peer device. It may be client software or a router.

hh3cDvpnSessionHisTable.name: hh3cDvpnSessionHisTable
hh3cDvpnSessionHisTable.description: The dvpn session history table. This table contains session's history information, include input/output packet number, up/down time, etc. This table will exist during the 'hh3cDvpnSessionHisAgeTime'.

hh3cDvpnSessionHisDvpnID.name: hh3cDvpnSessionHisDvpnID
hh3cDvpnSessionHisDvpnID.description: The ID of the dvpn domain which the session belongs to.

hh3cDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIPType.name: hh3cDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIPType
hh3cDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIPType.description: The private ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of session peer device.

hh3cDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIP.name: hh3cDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIP
hh3cDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIP.description: The private ip of the session peer device.

hh3cDvpnSessionHisSendPkt.name: hh3cDvpnSessionHisSendPkt
hh3cDvpnSessionHisSendPkt.description: The number of sent packets on the session.

hh3cDvpnSessionHisRcvPkt.name: hh3cDvpnSessionHisRcvPkt
hh3cDvpnSessionHisRcvPkt.description: The number of received packets on the session.

hh3cDvpnSessionHisOnlineNumber.name: hh3cDvpnSessionHisOnlineNumber
hh3cDvpnSessionHisOnlineNumber.description: The number of the session online.

hh3cDvpnSessionHisOnlineFlag.name: hh3cDvpnSessionHisOnlineFlag
hh3cDvpnSessionHisOnlineFlag.description: If the session is online, the value is 'yes'. If the session is not online, the value is 'no'.

hh3cDvpnSessionHisPeerDeviceId.name: hh3cDvpnSessionHisPeerDeviceId
hh3cDvpnSessionHisPeerDeviceId.description: The identifier of peer device. It is a string.

hh3cDvpnMibCompliance.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement the DVPN MIB.
